<p><strong>Bug B</strong> — The player should only jump when on the ground. Right now it can jump forever in mid-air ("flying").</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">if event.key == pygame.K_SPACE:
    velocity_y = JUMP_STRENGTH
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> add a condition so the jump only happens when <code>on_ground</code> is true.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
